<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> rā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>rā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>tevaṟku yāṇṭu 20 Āvatu kuṉṟakkūṟṟattu <hi rend="grantha">brahmade</hi>yam Iciṟupaḻuvūr tiruvālantuṟai <hi rend="grantha">mahā</hi>
<lb n="2"/><hi rend="grantha">de</hi>varkku vaṉā<unclear>nuṭe</unclear>yār teviyār nāṭṭaṉ ceyāḷ naṅkai vacca non <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> v<unclear>i</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="8" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="3"/><unclear>vai</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> 
</p>

